    - ncidd.whitelist.5: ncid-modules.7 new
    - ncidmodules.1, ncidmodules.conf.5, ncidtools.1 : removed
    - INSTALL-Cygwin: added rebase and service documentation
    - INSTALL-Fedora: added install section using yum
    - INSTALL-Mac: added section using launchctl
